title: PDC World Championship Darts [PC game] 6 language interface
description:
PDC World Championship Darts
----------------------------
Game for PC.
Copied DVD-ROM [exe]
No serial or fixes required.

REQUIREMENTS
------------
98/2000/XP.
2GHz CPU.
512 RAM.

QUICK GAME.
-----------
Play against the computer or a friend

STANDARD RULES
--------------
301/501/701

PARTY GAMEs.
-----------
Around the clock,
Around the clock reverse,
Around the clock doubles and trebles,
Black and white,
Cricket US,
Cricket UK,
Killer,
Knockout,
Odd Man Out,
Shanghai,
Fives,
Twenty One.

Tournaments.
------------
Save your games.

Player Editor
-------------
Name, shirt style and color, enhance music and control mechanism.

6 Language interface
--------------------
English, German, Italy, Spain, Dutch, French.

Delivered in rar folder contains:-
PDC World Championship Darts [exe],
Text document about game instructions.

Extract the game from the rar folder and run Setup.exe....easy peasy.

If you havent got a rar extractor installed, download one from the link provided, recommend 7Zip.
Once 7Zip has installed, simply right click on the downloaded rar folder > 7Zip > extract here.
